1 Home

1.1 sale

 Parameter description:

Cmd: command keyword, the default &quot;daily\_sale&quot;

Order: sort field, the default entity\_id

Desc: sort by ASC/DESCdefault desc in reverse order

Page: page number, the default is 1 page

Limit: units of data per page by default displays 20 items

 Default url:

[http://w.sunpop.cn/cn/restconnect/index/index/cmd/daily\_sale/order/name/dir/asc/limit/10/page/1](https://ssl.translatoruser.net/bv.aspx?from=zh-CHS&amp;to=en&amp;a=http%3A%2F%2Fw.sunpop.cn%2Fcn%2Frestconnect%2Findex%2Findex%2Fcmd%2Fdaily_sale%2Forder%2Fname%2Fdir%2Fasc%2Flimit%2F10%2Fpage%2F1)

Alternative URL format (?,&amp; the parameter formatting, the following are the same )

http://w.sunpop.cn/cn/restconnect/?cmd=daily\_sale&amp;page=1&amp;limit=10

 Return value:

| Type | Name | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| string | entity\_id | Product ID |
| string | type\_id | Product type(simple,group...) |
| string | sku | Product SKU |
| string | name | Product name |
| string | regular\_price\_with\_tax | Product price |
| string | final\_price\_with\_tax | The current price, that is, when a product is on sale when the specials, not in the period for the original price |
| string | special\_from\_date | Date starting from which the special price is applied to the product |
| string | special\_to\_date | Date till which the special price is applied to the product |
| string | url\_key | Relative URL path that can be entered in place of a target path |
| string | image\_url | Image URL |
